{{# Test looping over a JSON array passed directly as variable #}}
** JSON Array Loop **
{{for person in jsonarray}}
{{:person.@@index}}) {{:person.first_name}} {{:person.last_name}} (age {{:person.age}})
{{endfor}}

** With Pseudo Variables **
{{for p in jsonarray}}
{{:p.first_name}}: {{if p.@@odd}}ODD{{endif}}{{if p.@@even}}EVEN{{endif}}{{if p.@@first}} [FIRST]{{endif}}{{if p.@@last}} [LAST]{{endif}}
{{endfor}}

** Accessing Nested Objects **
{{for person in jsonarray}}
{{:person.first_name}} drives a {{:person.car.brand}} {{:person.car.model}}
{{endfor}}
